params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.file_name
params.description: The name of the generated file. The default is "manifest" with the extension suffix corresponding to the Manifest.type.

params.name: data.type
params.description: Required. Type of the manifest, can be "HLS" or "DASH".

params.name: data.mux_streams
params.description: Required. List of user given MuxStream.keys that should appear in this manifest. When Manifest.type is HLS, a media manifest with name MuxStream.key and .m3u8 extension is generated for each element of the Manifest.mux_streams.
